metadata.name: Genesis #0000
metadata.description: In this infinite universe, we hold the power to shape our own reality. The choices we make and the actions we take have the ability to shape the course of our lives and the lives of those around us. It is up to us to recognize the power we hold in our hands and use it to create a world that reflects our highest ideals and aspirations. Let us be the architects of our own destiny and work to build a better future for all.
